Open an existing draft in `$EDITOR` and re-save it in place under the same draft id. No new draft is created and nothing is discarded

Usage: mxr drafts edit <DRAFT_ID>

Arguments:
  <DRAFT_ID>  Draft ID to edit

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
